    "At the Center, Fax worked under sculptor Augusta Savage (1892-1962), who directed the Center, and alongside artists including Selma Burke and Norman Lewis.": [],
    "Fax\u2019s career roughly fell into two stages: the illustrator-cartoonist era and the author-chronicler era.": [],
